data.description: Super. Scintillating. Sensational. This Is The Ultimate in Contemporary Luxury a stone's throw from the highly desirable Patterson Park area. This quintessential diamond sits on a quite well maintained street in the Highland-town/Patterson Park area. Expertly designed and appointed this home exudes practical extravagance. Three (3) fully finished levels of bright space enhances the fluidity of this picturesque home! The sleek custom kitchen has been fully renovated and outfitted with stainless steel appliances and open concept. Dark oak engineered hardwood dawns the entire main and upper levels with luxury vinyl plank throughout the basement giving each level it's very own warmth, look and design. The lower level also features a fully finished bathroom with walk in shower  AND BEDROOM - Laundry area has ample storage space. Brand new HVAC system, Samsung washer/dryer set along with a open and flowing concept that is absolutely perfect for entertainment or special time with the family. For sure and for certain, this is all new where it counts -- electric, plumbing, HVAC and much more! Walk out from both the lower and main level to a freshly refinished deck and fenced back yard; the perfect place for morning coffee, tea or evening BBQ. There are a plethora of phenomenal options to choose from for relaxation making this home its own personal oasis. On the top floor there are 2 bedrooms each with their own full bathroom with tastefully chosen and exquisitely installed tile work  - the master suite boasts a full wall walk-in closet with room for entertaining or getting away into your own oasis inside of the masterfully designed home. No aspect has been overlooked as this house has been meticulously redesigned; immediately making this home the neighborhood's envy and the gold standard on the block. One thing for sure and two things for certain; this one is not going to last - why wait to see the rest when you have undoubtedly seen the best. Bring your best offer Your New Home Awaits Your Arrival.
